---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PortraitFrame from '../components/PortraitFrame.astro';
import portrait from '../assets/images/yannik-chair.jpg';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Yannik Kintscher"
  description="Senior fullstack engineer in Zürich. UBS Conversational Banking, internal platforms, applied AI."
  path="/about"
>
  <article class="about">
    <p class="meta">
      <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span>FILE&nbsp;/&nbsp;about</span>
      <span class="sep" aria-hidden="true">/</span>
      <time datetime="2026">2026</time>
      <span class="sep" aria-hidden="true">/</span>
      <span aria-label="Reading time: about 3 minutes">~3 min read</span>
    </p>

    <header class="about-head">
      <h1 class="about-title">
        <span class="line"><span class="line-inner">The long</span></span>
        <span class="line"><span class="line-inner"><em>version.</em></span></span>
      </h1>
      <p class="about-dek">
        <span class="line-inner">A short tour of the work, the route here, and what I’m chasing now.</span>
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="bio">
      <aside class="bio-rail" aria-label="Portrait marginalia">
        <PortraitFrame
          src={portrait}
          alt="Yannik Kintscher, seated"
          ariaLabel="Portrait of Yannik Kintscher"
          objectPosition="50% 32%"
          caption="PORTRAIT · ZÜRICH · 2026"
          index="02"
          sizes="(max-width: 720px) 78vw, (max-width: 900px) 460px, (max-width: 1099px) 340px, 420px"
          class="about-portrait"
        />

        <div class="rail-mid">
          <dl class="rail-status" aria-label="Status">
            <div class="rail-status-row">
              <dt>loc</dt>
              <span class="rail-status-sep" aria-hidden="true">:</span>
              <dd>zürich, ch</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="rail-status-row">
              <dt>role</dt>
              <span class="rail-status-sep" aria-hidden="true">:</span>
              <dd>sw eng @ ubs / conversational banking</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="rail-status-row">
              <dt>status</dt>
              <span class="rail-status-sep" aria-hidden="true">:</span>
              <dd>shipping, building, lifting</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>

          <p class="rail-manifesto">
            <span class="rail-manifesto-mark" aria-hidden="true">&gt;</span>
            <span class="rail-manifesto-text">building tools that make the day less tedious.</span>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rail-foot">
          <hr class="rail-rule" />
          <p class="rail-sig">
            <span class="rail-sig-name">Yannik Kintscher</span>
            <span class="rail-sig-sep" aria-hidden="true">/</span>
            <span class="rail-sig-loc">Zürich · CH</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="bio-text">
        <p class="bio-para">
          Came up the Swiss way: a 4-year
          <button type="button" class="annot" aria-describedby="gloss-efz">Informatiker EFZ<span class="tip" role="tooltip" id="gloss-efz">Swiss federal IT diploma. 4 years, dual-track.</span></button>
          apprenticeship at UBS. Year one was
          <button type="button" class="annot" aria-describedby="gloss-basic">Basic Training in Altstetten<span class="tip" role="tooltip" id="gloss-basic">UBS apprentice training centre. Pre-team year.</span></button>,
          covering IT fundamentals, Scrum, and group projects. The next three
          years I spent in Wealth Management on trading applications, building
          Java REST services and internal trading interfaces. That stretch
          taught me how high-stakes systems actually get built and shipped.
        </p>

        <p class="bio-para">
          Since 2022 I’ve been on the Conversational Banking team, working on
          the
          <button type="button" class="annot" aria-describedby="gloss-va">Virtual Assistant<span class="tip" role="tooltip" id="gloss-va">UBS E-Banking and Mobile Banking chatbot. Live for clients.</span></button>,
          UBS’s E-Banking and Mobile Banking chatbot. I started on the Java
          backend, owning services that powered the bot in production, and
          drove the Java side end-to-end into its first production release in
          2023. I was on the team before generative AI hit; when it did, I
          helped drive LLM integrations and
          <button type="button" class="annot" aria-describedby="gloss-aoi">Azure OpenAI<span class="tip" role="tooltip" id="gloss-aoi">Enterprise OpenAI on Azure. Compliant, governed.</span></button>
          adoption, shipping one of UBS’s first external GenAI use cases. In
          2024 I moved into fullstack by building the
          <button type="button" class="annot" aria-describedby="gloss-portal">Chatbot Portal<span class="tip" role="tooltip" id="gloss-portal">Internal platform. React and Python. Built it.</span></button>,
          a React and Python platform the team uses to monitor, analyze, and
          test the bot end-to-end, and shipped the first test automation suite
          in the Conversational Banking crew along the way. An internal
          rotation into
          <button type="button" class="annot" aria-describedby="gloss-speech">Speech Analytics<span class="tip" role="tooltip" id="gloss-speech">Sister team. NLP on call data. Short rotation.</span></button>
          that year gave me a first taste of NLP and shipped a new REST
          service into production. That same year I also won the
          <button type="button" class="annot" aria-describedby="gloss-hack">Microsoft × UBS THINK AHEAD GenAI Hackathon<span class="tip" role="tooltip" id="gloss-hack">Microsoft × UBS hackathon. We won.</span></button>
          with a cross-team squad, and was promoted to
          <button type="button" class="annot" aria-describedby="gloss-auth">Authorized Officer<span class="tip" role="tooltip" id="gloss-auth">UBS title rank. Bumped up in spring 2025.</span></button>
          the following spring.
        </p>

        <p class="bio-para">
          Right now I’m most interested in agents and applied AI, tooling
          that makes developer workflows faster and day-to-day work less
          tedious. The Chatbot Portal is one example, and I want to do more
          of that. Currently shipping evaluation and data-labelling tooling
          for the Virtual Assistant, tinkering on side projects in the
          evenings, and going deep on agent architectures.
        </p>

        <p class="signoff"><em>— Y.</em></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="stack" aria-labelledby="stack-h">
      <header class="stack-head">
        <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <h2 id="stack-h" class="stack-kicker">§&nbsp;Stack</h2>
        <span class="sep" aria-hidden="true">/</span>
        <span class="stack-meta">tools I trust, tools I’m watching</span>
      </header>

      <dl class="stack-list">
        <div class="stack-row">
          <dt><em>Daily</em></dt>
          <dd>
            <span>Python</span><span class="dot-sep">·</span>
            <span>TypeScript</span><span class="dot-sep">·</span>
            <span>React</span><span class="dot-sep">·</span>
            <span>FastAPI</span>
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-row">
          <dt><em>Backend &amp; infra</em></dt>
          <dd>
            <span>Azure</span><span class="dot-sep">·</span>
            <span>OpenAI</span><span class="dot-sep">·</span>
            <span>Postgres</span><span class="dot-sep">·</span>
            <span>Redis</span><span class="dot-sep">·</span>
            <span>GitLab&nbsp;CI</span>
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-row">
          <dt><em>Exploring</em></dt>
          <dd>
            <span>LangGraph</span><span class="dot-sep">·</span>
            <span>Agent tooling</span><span class="dot-sep">·</span>
            <span>Cloudflare&nbsp;Workers</span>
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </section>

    <footer class="about-foot">
      <a class="next-link" href="/chat">
        <span class="next-kicker">next&nbsp;/</span>
        <span class="next-label">ask yannik anything</span>
        <span class="next-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        <span class="key-hint" aria-hidden="true">⌘&nbsp;C</span>
      </a>
    </footer>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ───────────────────────────── shell ───────────────────────────── */

  .about {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding: clamp(2.5rem, 6vh, 5rem) clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 2.5rem) clamp(3rem, 7vh, 6rem);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    row-gap: clamp(2rem, 4.5vh, 3.5rem);
  }

  /* very soft warm wash to lift the page out of pure black */
  .about::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    background:
      radial-gradient(60% 50% at 18% 22%, rgb(232 168 58 / 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(40% 30% at 82% 88%, rgb(91 168 155 / 0.035) 0%, transparent 70%);
    z-index: -1;
  }

  /* ───────────────────────────── meta ───────────────────────────── */

  .meta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-quiet);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-up 380ms cubic-bezier(0.5, 0, 0.2, 1) 80ms both;
  }
  .meta .dot {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--color-signal);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgb(91 168 155 / 0.6);
    animation: pulse-signal 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .meta .sep { color: var(--color-quiet); opacity: 0.5; }

  /* ───────────────────────────── headline ───────────────────────────── */

  .about-head {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 24ch;
  }

  .about-title {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 7vw, 5.75rem);
    line-height: 0.96;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--color-fg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .about-title .line { display: block; overflow: hidden; }
  .about-title .line-inner {
    display: inline-block;
    transform: translateY(105%);
    animation: rise 720ms cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.7, 0, 1) both;
  }
  .about-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--color-fg); }
  .about-title .line:nth-child(1) .line-inner { animation-delay: 180ms; }
  .about-title .line:nth-child(2) .line-inner { animation-delay: 280ms; }

  .about-dek {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.05vw, 1.0625rem);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    max-width: 38ch;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .about-dek .line-inner {
    display: inline-block;
    transform: translateY(105%);
    animation: rise 720ms cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.7, 0, 1) 420ms both;
  }

  /* ───────────────────────────── bio (portrait + text) ───────────────────────────── */

  .bio {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(280px, 420px) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4rem);
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  /* Left rail — image at top, signature at bottom, metadata + pull-quote
     distribute through the middle. The rail stretches to match the bio
     text height so the column never goes dead. */
  .bio-rail {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: clamp(1.75rem, 3vh, 2.5rem);
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .about-portrait {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-up 800ms cubic-bezier(0.5, 0, 0.2, 1) 600ms both;
  }

  .rail-mid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: clamp(1.25rem, 3vh, 2.25rem);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-up 720ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) 820ms both;
  }

  /* Terminal-style status block — reads as a whoami / status line. */
  .rail-status {
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    color: var(--color-quiet);
  }
  .rail-status-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3.25rem auto minmax(0, 1fr);
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .rail-status-row dt,
  .rail-status-row dd { margin: 0; }
  .rail-status-row dt { color: var(--color-quiet); opacity: 0.7; }
  .rail-status-sep { color: var(--color-quiet); opacity: 0.55; }
  .rail-status-row dd {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    overflow-wrap: break-word;
  }

  /* Single-line manifesto — shell-prompt cue, mono, dim. */
  .rail-manifesto {
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: clamp(13px, 1vw, 14px);
    line-height: 1.5;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    max-width: 32ch;
  }
  .rail-manifesto-mark {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.85;
  }
  .rail-manifesto-text { color: var(--color-muted); }

  .rail-foot {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-up 720ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) 980ms both;
  }
  .rail-rule {
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    border: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);
  }
  .rail-sig {
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-quiet);
  }
  .rail-sig-name { color: var(--color-muted); }
  .rail-sig-sep { color: var(--color-quiet); opacity: 0.5; }
  .rail-sig-loc { color: var(--color-quiet); }

  /* ───────────────────────────── bio text ───────────────────────────── */

  .bio-text {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.4em;
    /* fill the grid column; constrain measure on each paragraph */
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .bio-para {
    position: relative;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 54ch;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: clamp(1.0625rem, 1.05vw, 1.125rem);
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: rgb(240 235 226 / 0.82);
    letter-spacing: 0.002em;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-up 720ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) both;
  }

  /* On wide viewports, shift the bio column right to reserve a left margin
     where the gloss can render without colliding with the portrait. */
  @media (min-width: 1100px) {
    .bio-para,
    .signoff { margin-left: 5.5rem; }
  }
  .bio-para:nth-of-type(1) { animation-delay: 520ms; }
  .bio-para:nth-of-type(2) { animation-delay: 640ms; }
  .bio-para:nth-of-type(3) { animation-delay: 760ms; }

  /* drop-cap on the first paragraph for editorial warmth */
  .bio-para:first-of-type::first-letter {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 3.4em;
    line-height: 0.85;
    float: left;
    padding: 0.18em 0.18em 0 0;
    color: var(--color-fg);
  }

  .signoff {
    margin-top: 0.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    margin-right: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 1.8vw, 1.9rem);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-up 720ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) 980ms both;
  }
  .signoff em { font-style: italic; }

  /* ───────────────────────────── annotations ───────────────────────────── */

  .annot {
    /* button reset — keeps the term flowing as inline prose */
    appearance: none;
    -webkit-appearance: none;
    background-color: transparent;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    font: inherit;
    color: var(--color-fg);
    line-height: inherit;
    text-align: inherit;
    display: inline;

    position: relative;
    background-image: linear-gradient(transparent 0%, transparent calc(100% - 1px), var(--color-hairline-strong) calc(100% - 1px));
    background-size: 100% 100%;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    cursor: help;
    transition: color 160ms ease, background-image 160ms ease;
  }
  .annot::after {
    content: '°';
    position: relative;
    top: -0.25em;
    margin-left: 0.1em;
    font-size: 0.7em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.45;
    transition: opacity 160ms ease, transform 160ms ease;
  }
  .annot:hover,
  .annot:focus-visible {
    color: var(--color-fg);
    background-image: linear-gradient(transparent 0%, transparent calc(100% - 1px), var(--color-accent) calc(100% - 1px));
    outline: none;
  }
  .annot:hover::after,
  .annot:focus-visible::after { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(-1px); }

  /* tooltip — readable card that floats below the term */
  .tip {
    position: absolute;
    top: calc(100% + 0.55rem);
    left: 0;
    z-index: 10;
    width: max-content;
    max-width: min(22rem, calc(100vw - 2rem));
    padding: 0.6rem 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline-strong);
    border-left: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: rgb(20 20 24 / 0.96);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    box-shadow:
      0 1px 0 rgb(255 255 255 / 0.04) inset,
      0 12px 28px -12px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.7),
      0 4px 12px -6px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.5);

    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    letter-spacing: 0.002em;
    color: var(--color-fg);
    text-align: left;
    white-space: normal;

    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 160ms ease, transform 200ms cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.7, 0, 1);
  }
  /* small caret pointing up to the term */
  .tip::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -5px;
    left: 0.85rem;
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: rgb(20 20 24 / 0.96);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline-strong);
    border-left: 1px solid var(--color-hairline-strong);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .annot:hover .tip,
  .annot:focus-visible .tip {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* keep tooltip from clipping past the right edge of long terms near viewport edge */
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .tip { left: 0; right: auto; max-width: calc(100vw - 2rem); }
  }

  /* ───────────────────────────── stack ───────────────────────────── */

  .stack {
    margin-top: clamp(0.5rem, 2vh, 1.5rem);
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-up 720ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) 1100ms both;
  }

  .stack-head {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-quiet);
  }
  .stack-head .dot {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--color-signal);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgb(91 168 155 / 0.6);
    animation: pulse-signal 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .stack-head .sep { color: var(--color-quiet); opacity: 0.5; }
  .stack-kicker {
    margin: 0;
    font: inherit;
    color: var(--color-fg);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .stack-meta { color: var(--color-quiet); }

  .stack-list { margin: 0; padding: 0; display: grid; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .stack-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(11rem, 14rem) 1fr;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    padding: 0.7rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);
  }
  .stack-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .stack-row dt {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 1.6vw, 1.6rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--color-fg);
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .stack-row dt em { font-style: italic; }

  .stack-row dd {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    column-gap: 0.55rem;
    row-gap: 0.25rem;
    align-items: baseline;
  }
  .stack-row dd .dot-sep {
    color: var(--color-quiet);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
  .stack-row dd > span:not(.dot-sep) {
    color: var(--color-fg);
    transition: color 160ms ease;
  }
  .stack-row:hover dd > span:not(.dot-sep) { color: var(--color-fg); }

  /* ───────────────────────────── next-link ───────────────────────────── */

  .about-foot {
    margin-top: clamp(2rem, 4vh, 3rem);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-up 720ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) 1240ms both;
  }
  .next-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 160ms ease, gap 220ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }
  .next-kicker { color: var(--color-quiet); letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .next-label  { color: var(--color-fg); }
  .next-arrow  { color: var(--color-accent); transition: transform 220ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1); }
  .next-link:hover { gap: 1rem; }
  .next-link:hover .next-arrow { transform: translateX(3px); }
  .next-link:hover .next-label { color: var(--color-fg); }

  /* ───────────────────────────── animations ───────────────────────────── */

  @keyframes rise { to { transform: translateY(0); } }
  @keyframes fade-up {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes pulse-signal {
    0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgb(91 168 155 / 0.45); opacity: 1; }
    50%      { box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgb(91 168 155 / 0.85); opacity: 0.75; }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .meta, .about-title .line-inner, .about-dek .line-inner,
